"""
gh-mcp: MCP server wrapping the gh CLI for zero-PAT GitHub access.

Uses the existing `gh auth` OAuth session — no tokens stored, read, or
exposed in Claude's context. Token never appears in conversation history.

Install: add to ~/.claude/settings.json mcpServers (see README)
Requires: gh CLI authenticated via `gh auth login`
"""
